 Apoclaaypse sent a comm to his troops ordering them to mobilize infront of 
the base. "They cant see us comeing by scan because of the jamming zone made 
by Magnus. Luckly it is on the edge of the zone." He nodded his head and and 
held out his hand. "To the new empire. The only empire."
